 como la importancia que tiene el ahorro para&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">cualquier conductor.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><em>Carrazo</em>, es un apasionado de la conservaci&oacute;n ambiental y el combate a la contaminaci&oacute;n; le gusta&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">la responsabilidad y seguridad de automovilistas y peatones. T</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">e ayudara a cuidar t&uacute; auto junto con &nbsp;<em>Beb&eacute; Vagoneta, Ferrato, Forzon, Mustanguia, Porschia, Taxilio, Tsuru San, Wagoneta y Voshito.</em></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','',1,52,'2014-09-26 21:41:57',451,'','2014-11-18 05:23:50',451,451,'2014-11-18 05:23:50','2014-09-26 21:42:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/carrazo-bardahl.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"Carrazo......\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"t3_bs3_blank:articles\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',8,0,'','',1,22,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*','