ize: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;\\\">productos industriales<\\/em><span style=\\\"font-family: sans-serif, Arial, Verdana, \'Trebuchet MS\'; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;\\\">. Estamos comprometidos con el constante&nbsp;<\\/span><strong style=\\\"font-family: sans-serif, Arial, Verdana, \'Trebuchet MS\'; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;\\\">desarrollo<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-family: sans-serif, Arial, Verdana, \'Trebuchet MS\'; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;\\\">&nbsp;de nuevos y mejores productos para los motores y necesidades de nuestros clientes, cuya satisfacci&oacute;n es nuestra &uacute;nica misi&oacute;n.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<p>\\r\\n\\t\\tEstamos conscientes del compromiso que adquirimos con ustedes desde hace&nbsp;<strong>62 a&ntilde;os<\\/strong>, por lo que tambi&eacute;n estamos agradecidos. Creemos que la mejor forma de darles las gracias es proporcionar&nbsp;los mejores productos y&nbsp;<em>fluidos automotrices<\\/em>&nbsp;para que su auto est&eacute; en condiciones optimas. Sabiendo que&nbsp;<strong>todo anda bien con Bardahl.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"12\",\"created\":\"2014-10-14 15:54:00\",\"created_by\":\"451\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-14 23:22:31\",\"modified_by\":\"451\",\"checked_out\":\"451\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2014-10-14 23:22:14\",\"publish_up\":\"2014-10-14 15:54:00\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"