0-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":null,\"urls\":null,\"hits\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"version\":\"1\",\"publish_up\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\"}',0),(427,92,1,'','2014-10-14 23:51:50',451,3824,'f123aea4d4b6dd078b245bbd8df7f1def94e5cba','{\"id\":92,\"asset_id\":284,\"title\":\"La importancia del inyector\",\"alias\":\"la-importancia-del-inyector\",\"introtext\":\"<h3>\\r\\n\\t<strong>La importancia del inyector<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t<span style=\\\"line-height: 1.6em;\\\">Los <em>inyectores<\\/em>, son elementos fundamentales en el sistema de combusti&oacute;n; aunque utilice gasolina de alto octanaje (Premium&nbsp; 92 octanos), su sistema de combusti&oacute;n est&aacute; expuesto a la acumulaci&oacute;n de suciedad y residuos que provocan problemas en el sistema y en su econom&iacute;a. El inyector pulveriza la gasolina, lo que permite una mezcla ideal para la combusti&oacute;n y un eficiente encendido.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t<span style=\\\"line-height: 1.6em;\\\">Ambas gasolinas, Magna y Premium, contienen impurezas y traen como consecuencia <em>&nbsp;inyectores sucios<\\/em>, v&aacute;lvulas de admisi&oacute;n carbonizadas, convertidores catal&iacute;ticos contaminados, etc&hellip; La atomizaci&oacute;n del combustible, ser&aacute; deficiente; ocasionando una<em> mala combusti&oacute;n<\\/em>, jaloneos, falta de potencia, dificultad al encenderlo y mayores emisiones. Para remediar este da&ntilde;o (el cual puede ser costoso), tendr&aacute; que llevar el auto al taller para una <strong>limpieza de inyectores<\\/strong> con boya, prescindir del auto, etc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t<span style=\\\"line-height: 1.6em;\\\">Es por eso que recomendamos, siempre llenar el tanque de combustible con un aditivo<strong> Nanox de Bardahl<\\/strong>, de tal forma que el sistema se mantendr&aacute; limpio por m&aacute;s tiempo y con mayor gasolina se <em>minimiza la presencia de agua en el tanque<\\/em>, evitando oxido ferroso (polvo de metal) que puede obstruir los inyectores. &nbsp;De ese modo, la <em>bomba de combustible<\\/em> durar&aacute; m&aacute;s tiempo debido a que la gasolina disipa el calor de la misma y la lubrica al mismo tiempo <strong>(no dejar el tanque con menos de &frac14;)<\\/strong>. Evite contratiempos y gastos innecesarios.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t<img alt=\\\"Top Oil Bardahl\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/frikslabs.com\\/bardahl\\/images\\/top-oil-bardahl.jpg\\\" title=\\\"Top Oil Bardahl\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"42\",\"created\":\"2014-10-14 18:46:05\",\"created_by\":\"451\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-14 23:51:50\",\"modified_by\":\"451\",\"checked_out\":\"451\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2014-10-14 23:46:05\",\"publish_up\":\"2014-10-14 23:51:50\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":2,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0),(428,39,1,'','2014-10-15 02:07:23',451,2337,'3a6286ffbc0cb8d3fd872f6a408cd54c3cad6227','{\"id\":\"39\",\"asset_id\":286,\"title\":\"Bardahl Motos 2T JASO  FB\",\"alias\":\"bardahl-motos-2t-jaso-fb\",\"introtext\":\"<h3>\\u00bfQu\\u00e9 es?<\\/h3><p>Aditivo lubricante diluible en gasolina para motores de 2 tiempos.<\\/p><h3>\\u00bfPara qu\\u00e9 tipo de veh\\u00edculo se recomienda?<\\/h3><p>Para Motocicletas de 2 tiempos.<\\/p><h3>Beneficios<\\/h3><p>Disminuye al m\\u00e1ximo las emisiones contaminantes. Para motores a 2 tiempos enfriados por aire (motos, motosierras, plantas de luz, equipo de jardiner\\u00eda), evita el desgaste prematuro del motor, se mezcla eficazmente con la gasolina.<\\/p><h3>Recomendaciones de Uso<\\/h3><p>Agregar 250 ml por cada 5 litros de gasolina o lo que indique el manual del equipo. En cada carga de gasolina se debe agregar el aditivo lubricante. Se coloca en el dep\\u00f3sito para aceite o en el tanque de gasolina dependiendo del modelo.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":63,\"created\":\"2014-10-14 19:40:09\",\"created_by\":\"0\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-15 02:07:23\",\"modified_by\":\"451\",\"checked_out\":\"0\",\"checked_out_time\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"publish_up\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/icon\\\\\\/bardahl-motos-2t-jaso-fb.jpg\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"Bardahl Motos 2T JASO  FB\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"t3_bs3_blank:producto\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":\"1\",\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0),(429,40,1,'','2014-10-15 02:07:23',451,2585,'6388e2dc92588801473a316a5390fc0b9cf47133','{\"id\":\"40\",\"asset_id\":287,\"title\":\"Bardahl Motos 4T JASO\",\"alias\":\"bardahl-motos-4t-jaso\",\"introtext\":\"<h3>\\u00bfQu\\u00e9 es?<\\/h3><p>Bardahl \\u00ae Motos 4T SAE 20W-50 API SL es un lubricante multigrado de base mineral, para motocicletas de 4 Tiempos en servicio de carretera o urbano. Satisface los requerimientos de los principales fabricantes de motos de 4 tiempos europeos y japoneses.<\\/p><h3>\\u00bfPara qu\\u00e9 tipo de veh\\u00edculo se recomienda?<\\/h3><p>Para motocicletas de 4 tiempos.<\\/p><h3>Beneficios<\\/h3><p>Por su elevada detergencia asegura una excelente limpieza del pist\\u00f3n. Adecuada protecci\\u00f3n durante el arranque y elevada protecci\\u00f3n de pel\\u00edcula lubricante a altas temperaturas. Mantiene una excelente lubricaci\\u00f3n en toda \\u00e9poca del a\\u00f1o, asegurando una m\\u00e1xima protecci\\u00f3n contra el gripado del pist\\u00f3n.<\\/p><h3>Recomendaciones de Uso<\\/h3><p>Recomendado para Motos de 4 tiempos de cualquier cilindrada y prestaciones. Indicado para conducci\\u00f3n severa. Para motores con lubricaci\\u00f3n conjunta del motor, caja de cambios y embrague h\\u00famedo.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":63,\"created\":\"2014-10-14 19:40:09\",\"created_by\":\"0\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-15 02:07:23\",\"modified_by\":\"451\",\"checked_out\":\"0\",\"checked_out_time\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"publish_up\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/icon\\\\\\/bardahl-motos-4t-jaso.jpg\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"Bardahl Motos 4T JASO\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\