ervicio ligero y veh\\u00edculos fuera de carretera.<\\/p><h3>Beneficios<\\/h3><p>Buena resistencia a la degradaci\\u00f3n t\\u00e9rmica y a la oxidaci\\u00f3n, alargando la vida del aceite y la protecci\\u00f3n a los mecanismos. Buena fluidez a muy bajas temperaturas, asegurando una pel\\u00edcula lubricante de todos los mecanismos de las cajas autom\\u00e1ticas. Alta protecci\\u00f3n contra el desgaste, maximizando la vida del equipo.<\\/p><h3>Recomendaciones de Uso<\\/h3><p>Cajas de Transmisi\\u00f3n Autom\\u00e1tica de autom\\u00f3viles, camiones de servicio ligero, y veh\\u00edculos fuera de carretera donde el fabricante recomiende el uso de un aceite con especificaci\\u00f3n DEXRON II. Bombas de direcci\\u00f3n hidr\\u00e1ulica automotrices. Sistemas hidr\\u00e1ulicos como: Sperry Vickers, Denison y Sundstrand.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":64,\"created\":\"2014-10-14 19:40:09\",\"created_by\":\"0\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-15 08:04:29\",\"modified_by\":\"451\",\"checked_out\":\"0\",\"checked_out_time\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"publish_up\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/icon\\\\\\/bardahl-atf.jpg\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"Bardahl ATF \\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_ite