 aditivos para motor de <strong>Bardahl<\\/strong> son recomendables para cualquier veh&iacute;culo. El <em>aceite lubrica<\\/em> (separando las superficies de los metales) y reduce la fricci&oacute;n permitiendo que el motor funcione adecuadamente. Sin embargo, la falta de lubricaci&oacute;n existe en ciertos momentos cr&iacute;ticos, es ah&iacute; &nbsp;donde entran los <em>aditivos<\\/em>. El desgaste m&aacute;s severo del motor es al encenderlo (arranque en fr&iacute;o o en seco); al revolucionarlo, la pel&iacute;cula de aceite se rompe, de tal forma que este sufrir&aacute; desgaste. El aditivo <strong>Bardahl 1<\\/strong> forma una pel&iacute;cula &ldquo;magn&eacute;tica&rdquo; o atracci&oacute;n polar permitiendo <em>minimizar el desgaste.<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t<span style=\\\"line-height: 1.6em;\\\">Por m&aacute;s de <strong>60 a&ntilde;os<\\/strong>, este aditivo ha cuidado el auto de miles de conductores, evitando desgaste prematuro y gastos excesivos por reparaciones mayores (ajustes).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t<span style=\\\"line-height: 1.6em;\\\">Util&iacute;celo en cada cambio de aceite, del 10 al 20% (si la capacidad es de 4 lts de aceite, ponga 3 &frac12; de aceite y una lata de 450 ml. de B1; s&iacute; es de seis a ocho cilindros el 20%, lata de 950 ml. de B1), sin importar si es <em>sint&eacute;tico, mineral, monogrado o multigrado<\\/em>. Es compatible con cualquier marca de<em> lubricante<\\/em> y de auto. Tambi&eacute;n &uacute;selo para rellenar el nivel del aceite.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t<span style=\\\"line-height: 1.6em;\\\">Al armar una m&aacute;quina, impregne el interior con <strong>Bardahl 1<\\/strong>, as&iacute; estar&aacute; protegida mucho antes de encenderla por primera vez.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t<img alt=\\\"Aditivo Bardahl 1\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/frikslabs.com\\/bardahl\\/images\\/aditivos-bardahl1.jpg\\\" title=\\\"Aditivo Bardahl 1\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"42\",\"created\":\"2014-10-14 18:35:39\",\"created_by\":\"451\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-11-18 00:54:59\",\"modified_by\":\"451\",\"checked_out\":\"451\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2014-11-18 00:54:34\",\"publish_up\":\"2014-10-14 23:43:10\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/Historia-bardahl.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":5,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"2\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",